# Pine City Zoo App

A multi-page zoo web application developed during the FNB App Academy programme.

## Features

- Interactive zoo navigation experience
- Animal information pages
- Weather section for visitor planning
- User-friendly interface design
- Multi-page application structure

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Skills Demonstrated

- Frontend development
- Responsive UI design
- Navigation structures
- User experience principles
- Web application organisation

